          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*mqnSigNYdPdKRIl2Ed6uWg.png",
          "alt": "post image"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "We are LIVE with ISSUE SIXTEEN of our DIGIFIZZY Zine!"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "For this month, we couldn’t help ourselves but to show you a taste of what the end of creative scarcity means— not just for artworks, photos and written content, but for fabrics and patterns and entire worlds conveyed across every medium we can imagine."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "Flip through the pages of CC0 open Stable Diffusion content made with unique prompts of elements and terms that make up the bedrock of everything in the DIGITALAX ecosystem."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "p",
          "value": "See how many of them you can spot 😉"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "You can check out issue 16 of here."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "tag": "h3",
          "value": "Join the DIGITALAX Discord to Stay Up to Date."
        },
        {
